(# Ride Completion, Cash Collection, GST, and Wallet Flow) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Scope) Tj
T*
(This document explains the current implementation for:) Tj
T*
(- Ride completion financial calculations) Tj
T*
(- GST extraction logic) Tj
T*
(- Cash vs QR collection behavior) Tj
T*
(- Wallet updates, constraints, and transaction history) Tj
T*
(- Key methods and storage involved in the flow) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## High-Level Flow) Tj
T*
(1. Captain accepts an order.) Tj
T*
(2. Trip progresses through pickup, OTP verification, navigation, and trip completion.) Tj
T*
(3. `RideCompletedScreen` computes/normalizes monetary values and persists payment details.) Tj
T*
(4. Captain collects payment via one of two options:) Tj
T*
(   - `Collect Cash`) Tj
T*
(   - `Collect via QR`) Tj
T*
(5. Wallet is updated differently based on collection mode.) Tj
T*
(6. Captain submits rating; session is archived and flow returns to Home.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Lifecycle and Method Trace) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### 1\) Order accepted) Tj
T*
(- File: `lib/features/home/presentation/pages/available_orders_page.dart`) Tj
T*
(- Methods:) Tj
T*
(  - `RideHistoryStore.startTrip\(...\)`) Tj
T*
(  - `TripSessionStore.startSession\(...\)`) Tj
T*
(- What gets saved:) Tj
T*
(  - Initial fare/distance labels) Tj
T*
(  - Pickup/drop addresses) Tj
T*
(  - Active trip identifiers) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### 2\) Trip progression) Tj
T*
(- Files:) Tj
T*
(  - `ride_arrived_page.dart` -> `RideHistoryStore.markPickedUpNow\(\)`,) Tj
T*
(`TripSessionStore.markArrivedAtPickup\(\)`) Tj
T*
(  - `enter_ride_code_page.dart` -> `RideHistoryStore.markStartedNow\(\)`,) Tj
T*
(`TripSessionStore.markTripStarted\(...\)`) Tj
T*
(  - `passenger_onboard_page.dart` -> `TripSessionStore.markNavigationBegan\(...\)`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### 3\) Trip completed) Tj
T*
(- File: `lib/features/home/presentation/pages/trip_navigation_page.dart`) Tj
T*
(- On complete action:) Tj
T*
(  - `TripSessionStore.markTripCompleted\(\)`) Tj
T*
(  - `RideHistoryStore.markCompletedNowOrCreate\(...\)`) Tj
T*
(  - Navigate to `RideCompletedScreen`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### 4\) Ride completed calculation sync) Tj
T*
(- File: `lib/features/ride_complete/presentation/pages/ride_completed_screen.dart`) Tj
T*
(- Startup method: `_syncSummaryAndPersist\(\)`) Tj
ET

endstream
