14 TL
(- It performs:) Tj
T*
(  - Summary normalization from active session fare/distance when needed) Tj
T*
(  - GST extraction) Tj
T*
(  - Net earning recomputation) Tj
T*
(  - `RideHistoryStore.updateLatestCompletedDetails\(...\)`) Tj
T*
(  - `TripSessionStore.savePaymentDetails\(...\)`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### 5\) Collection action \(cash/QR\)) Tj
T*
(- Same file: `ride_completed_screen.dart`) Tj
T*
(- Method: `_onCollectPaymentTap\({required bool viaQr, ...}\)`) Tj
T*
(- Behavior:) Tj
T*
(  - `viaQr == true`:) Tj
T*
(    - Add full collectable amount to wallet: `DriverWalletStore.addAmount\(totalCollectable\)`) Tj
T*
(    - Mark payment received: `TripSessionStore.markPaymentReceived\(method: 'online'\)`) Tj
T*
(  - `viaQr == false` \(cash\):) Tj
T*
(    - Subtract GST amount from wallet:) Tj
T*
(      - `next = currentWallet - gstAmount`) Tj
T*
(      - bounded by minimum allowed wallet balance \(`-50.0`\)) Tj
T*
(    - Save wallet: `DriverWalletStore.saveBalance\(bounded\)`) Tj
T*
(    - Mark payment received: `TripSessionStore.markPaymentReceived\(method: 'cash'\)`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### 6\) Feedback and closeout) Tj
T*
(- File: `lib/features/ride_complete/presentation/pages/rate_experience_screen.dart`) Tj
T*
(- On submit:) Tj
T*
(  - `TripSessionStore.savePassengerRating\(...\)` -> stage becomes `rated`, session archived) Tj
T*
(  - `RateExperienceCubit.submitFeedback\(\)`) Tj
T*
(  - `HomeTripResumeStore.clear\(\)` and navigate Home) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Financial Formula Definitions \(Current Implementation\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### A\) Collectable subtotal) Tj
T*
(- Method: `_collectableSubTotal\(...\)`) Tj
T*
(- Formula:) Tj
T*
(  - `collectableSubTotal = tripFare + tips - discountAmount`) Tj
T*
(  - If result <= 0, force `0`) Tj
T*
(  - Rounded to 2 decimals) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### B\) GST amount \(inclusive extraction\)) Tj
T*
(- Method: `_gstAmount\(...\)`) Tj
T*
(- Constants:) Tj
T*
(  - `_gstRate = 0.05` \(5%\)) Tj
T*
(- Formula used:) Tj
T*
(  - `gstAmount = \(collectableSubTotal * 0.05\) / 1.05`) Tj
T*
(  - Rounded to 2 decimals) Tj
T*
(- Note:) Tj
T*
(  - UI shows this as `GST \(5%\) ... \(included\)`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### C\) Net earning shown/persisted) Tj
T*
(- In `_syncSummaryAndPersist\(\)`:) Tj
T*
(  - `grossEarning` is taken from summary or fallback derivation) Tj
ET

endstream
