14 TL
(  - `netEarning = grossEarning - gstAmount`) Tj
T*
(  - Floor at `0`) Tj
T*
(- Saved to:) Tj
T*
(  - `RideHistoryStore.updateLatestCompletedDetails\(... netEarningAmount: netEarning\)`) Tj
T*
(  - `TripSessionStore.savePaymentDetails\(totalEarnings: netEarning, ...\)`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### D\) Incentive derivation fallback) Tj
T*
(- Method: `_deriveIncentive\(...\)`) Tj
T*
(- Formula:) Tj
T*
(  - `incentive = summary.totalEarnings - tripAmount + discountAmount`) Tj
T*
(  - If negative, force `0`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### E\) Gross earning fallback derivation) Tj
T*
(- Method: `_deriveNetEarning\(...\)` \(name is legacy; it computes gross fallback first\)) Tj
T*
(- Formula:) Tj
T*
(  - If `summary.totalEarnings > 0`: use it) Tj
T*
(  - Else: `tripAmount + incentiveAmount - discountAmount`) Tj
T*
(  - If negative, force `0`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Wallet Rules) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Wallet store behavior) Tj
T*
(- File: `lib/core/storage/driver_wallet_store.dart`) Tj
T*
(- Rules:) Tj
T*
(  - Key: `driver_wallet_balance_v1`) Tj
T*
(  - Minimum allowed balance: `-50.0`) Tj
T*
(  - `addAmount\(x\)` adds if `x > 0`) Tj
T*
(  - `subtractAmount\(x\)` returns `null` if result would go below `-50.0`) Tj
T*
(  - `saveBalance\(amount\)` clamps below `-50.0` to `-50.0`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Duty threshold behavior) Tj
T*
(- File: `lib/features/home/presentation/cubit/driver_status_state.dart`) Tj
T*
(- Constant: `kMinimumDutyWalletBalance = -50.0`) Tj
T*
(- At or below threshold can block going online and trigger warnings.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Earnings and Wallet Reporting) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Earnings snapshot source) Tj
T*
(- File: `lib/features/earnings/data/datasources/earnings_wallet_mock_api.dart`) Tj
T*
(- Snapshot computes:) Tj
T*
(  - `todaysEarnings`) Tj
T*
(  - `totalEarned`) Tj
T*
(  - `totalRides`) Tj
T*
(  - `walletBalance`) Tj
T*
(- Trip earning uses `EarningsCalculator.totalEarning\(...\)`.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Transaction list source) Tj
T*
(- Same file \(`earnings_wallet_mock_api.dart`\):) Tj
T*
(  - Trip earnings converted into credit transactions \(`WalletTransactionType.earning`\)) Tj
T*
(  - Recharge and withdrawal ops persisted under `earnings_wallet_ops_v1`) Tj
ET

endstream
