() Tj
T*
(## SharedPreferences Keys Used in This Flow) Tj
T*
(- `driver_wallet_balance_v1` \(wallet balance\)) Tj
T*
(- `ride_history_items_v1` \(ride history list\)) Tj
T*
(- `ride_history_active_trip_id_v1` \(active ride id\)) Tj
T*
(- `trip_session_active_v1` \(active trip session\)) Tj
T*
(- `trip_session_archive_v1` \(completed session archive\)) Tj
T*
(- `home_trip_resume_stage_v1` \(resume stage\)) Tj
T*
(- `home_trip_navigation_start_ms_v1` \(trip navigation time anchor\)) Tj
T*
(- `earnings_wallet_ops_v1` \(manual wallet recharge/withdraw operations\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Worked Example \(using current defaults\)) Tj
T*
(Given:) Tj
T*
(- Trip Fare = 1300) Tj
T*
(- Tips = 50) Tj
T*
(- Discount = 100) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Then:) Tj
T*
(1. `collectableSubTotal = 1300 + 50 - 100 = 1250`) Tj
T*
(2. `gstAmount = \(1250 * 0.05\) / 1.05 = 59.52` \(rounded\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(If captain taps:) Tj
T*
(- `Collect via QR`:) Tj
T*
(  - Wallet increases by `1250.00`) Tj
T*
(- `Collect Cash`:) Tj
T*
(  - Wallet decreases by `59.52` \(GST component only\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Important Implementation Notes) Tj
T*
(- GST is treated as included in collectable amount and extracted by inclusive formula.) Tj
T*
(- Cash and QR paths intentionally have different wallet effects.) Tj
T*
(- `RideCompletedScreen` currently owns a significant part of financial orchestration logic.) Tj
T*
(- Method naming note: `_deriveNetEarning` currently helps derive gross fallback before GST) Tj
T*
(deduction.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Suggested TL Talking Points) Tj
T*
(- Flow is fully persisted across app restarts via `RideHistoryStore`, `TripSessionStore`, and) Tj
T*
(`HomeTripResumeStore`.) Tj
T*
(- Financial logic is deterministic and concentrated in `RideCompletedScreen`.) Tj
T*
(- Wallet safety is enforced via minimum bound `-50.0`.) Tj
T*
(- Reporting screens \(`Earnings`, `Wallet`\) read computed history + wallet store and remain) Tj
T*
(consistent with persisted state.) Tj
ET

endstream
